5
(10)

6 hrs, 30 mins
·
Yield: 15
Make super crispy Masala Dosa at home with this step by step recipe! Best enjoyed with sambar and ...

Ingredients

3/4 cup sona masoori rice (or any raw or regular rice, 150 grams)3/4 cup idli rice (parboiled rice, 160 grams)1/2 cup urad dal gota (100 grams, dehusked whole urad dal or you can use urad dal dhuli (split urad dal))1 tablespoon chana dal (18 grams)1 tablespoon toor dal (18 grams)
